00:03:03.110 --> 00:03:04.500
[LAUGHING]

00:03:04.500 --> 00:03:06.750
AUDIENCE: I'm guessing
the answer's yes.

00:03:06.750 --> 00:03:10.660
ROBERT WRIGHT: No, it's a
